---
import Layout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Support Development | Mind Arc Games">
  <main class="support-page">
    <section class="support-hero">
      <p class="eyebrow">Support Phoenix Vector</p>

      <h1>Your support will help bring Phoenix Vector to launch.</h1>

      <p class="lead">
        Phoenix Vector is an independent sci-fi, side shooter built by Mind Arc
        Games. Your support helps fund development, testing, publishing costs,
        assets, tools, and the road toward the first public release.
      </p>

      <div class="support-actions">
        <a
          class="support-button support-button--primary"
          href="https://www.givesendgo.com/support-phoenix-vector?utm_source=sharelink&utm_medium=copy_link&utm_campaign=support-phoenix-vector"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener"
        >
          Support Development
        </a>

        <a
          class="support-button support-button--secondary"
          href="/phoenixvector"
        >
          Phoenix Vector
        </a>
      </div>

      <p class="support-note">Support is optional, but deeply appreciated.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="support-panel">
      <h2>What your support helps with</h2>

      <div class="support-grid">
        <article>
          <h3>Development Time</h3>
          <p>
            More focused time to build, polish, test, and prepare Phoenix Vector
            for release.
          </p>
        </article>

        <article>
          <h3>Publishing Costs</h3>
          <p>
            Platform fees, store preparation, mobile testing, and production
            expenses.
          </p>
        </article>

        <article>
          <h3>Creative Tools</h3>
          <p>
            Software, hardware, audio, visual assets, and systems needed to keep
            improving the game.
          </p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="founder-note">
      <div class="founder-profile">
        <img
          src="/images/joel.jpg"
          alt="Joel Mondesir, Founder of Mind Arc Games"
        />

        <div class="founder-info">
          <span class="founder-name">Joel Mondesir</span>
          <span class="founder-title">Founder, Mind Arc Games</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="founder-message">
        <h2>A Note from the Founder</h2>

        <p>
          I started creating Phoenix Vector with a simple question: “Could I
          build a great 2D shooter that was more than just mashing the fire
          button?” I was determined to build something original and thoughtful.
          It has been a long journey of learning new skills while sharpening old
          ones.
        </p>

        <p>
          Your support helps continue the development of Phoenix Vector and Mind
          Arc Games, moving us toward launch while remaining independent. From
          the bottom of my heart, thank you.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  .support-page {
    width: min(1120px, calc(100% - 2rem));
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 6rem) 0;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .support-hero {
    text-align: center;
    padding: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 4.5rem);
    border: 1px solid color-mix(in oklab, var(--border) 80%, transparent);
    border-radius: 1.5rem;
    background:
      radial-gradient(
        circle at top,
        color-mix(in oklab, var(--accent) 18%, transparent),
        transparent 45%
      ),
      color-mix(in oklab, var(--surface) 88%, transparent);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  }

  .eyebrow {
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .support-hero h1 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 7vw, 5rem);
    line-height: 0.95;
  }

  .lead {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 1.25rem auto 0;
    color: color-mix(in oklab, var(--text) 78%, transparent);
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 2.5vw, 1.2rem);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .support-actions {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.85rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .support-button {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    min-height: 46px;
    padding: 0.85rem 1.15rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 800;
    transition:
      transform 0.2s ease,
      border-color 0.2s ease,
      background-color 0.2s ease,
      color 0.2s ease;
  }

  .support-button:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .support-button--primary {
    color: color-mix(in oklab, var(--surface) 90%, black);
    background: var(--accent);
    border: 1px solid var(--accent);
  }

  .support-button--secondary {
    color: var(--text);
    border: 1px solid color-mix(in oklab, var(--border) 90%, transparent);
    background: color-mix(in oklab, var(--surface) 70%, transparent);
  }

  .support-note {
    margin: 1rem 0 0;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: color-mix(in oklab, var(--text) 65%, transparent);
  }

  .support-panel,
  .founder-note {
    margin-top: 1.25rem;
    padding: clamp(1.25rem, 4vw, 2rem);
    border: 1px solid color-mix(in oklab, var(--border) 75%, transparent);
    border-radius: 1.25rem;
    background: color-mix(in oklab, var(--surface) 82%, transparent);
  }

  .support-panel h2,
  .founder-note h2 {
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .support-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .support-grid article {
    padding: 1rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    background: color-mix(in oklab, var(--surface) 72%, black);
    border: 1px solid color-mix(in oklab, var(--border) 60%, transparent);
  }

  .support-grid h3 {
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
  }

  .support-grid p,
  .support-panel,
  .founder-note {
    margin-top: 1.25rem;
    padding: clamp(1.25rem, 4vw, 2rem);
    border: 1px solid color-mix(in oklab, var(--border) 75%, transparent);
    border-radius: 1.25rem;
    background: color-mix(in oklab, var(--surface) 82%, transparent);
  }

  .support-panel h2,
  .founder-note h2 {
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .support-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .support-grid article {
    padding: 1rem;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    background: color-mix(in oklab, var(--surface) 72%, black);
    border: 1px solid color-mix(in oklab, var(--border) 60%, transparent);
  }

  .support-grid h3 {
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
  }

  .support-grid p,
  .founder-note p {
    margin: 0;
    color: color-mix(in oklab, var(--text) 75%, transparent);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .founder-note {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .founder-profile {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .founder-profile img {
    width: 240px;
    height: 240px;

    display: block;

    object-fit: cover;

    border-radius: 12px;

    border: 2px solid cyan;
  }

  .founder-info {
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .founder-name {
    display: block;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .founder-title {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    opacity: 0.75;
  }

  .founder-message {
    flex: 1;
  }

  .founder-message p + p {
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 760px) {
    .support-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .support-button {
      width: 100%;
    }

    .founder-note {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .founder-profile {
      align-self: center;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 760px) {
    .support-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .support-button {
      width: 100%;
    }
  }
</style>
